snippet.title: Kantara Chapter 1 Trailer - Kannada | Rishab Shetty | Rukmini | Vijay Kiragandur | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
From Hombale Films ‚Äî the makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar ‚Äî and the visionary, National Award‚Äìwinning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies and a saga that will echo through generations. 

Witness India's Divine Epic on Screens this 2 October 2025.

snippet.title: Mahayoddha Rama - Official Teaser | The Epic Battle of Dharma vs Adharma | Releasing 17th Oct 2025
snippet.description:
üëâüèª SUBSCRIBE to Zee Music Company - https://bit.ly/ZeeMusicCo 

Contiloe Pictures presents Mahayoddha Rama ‚Äî a next-level 3D animated epic inspired by the timeless Ramayan. Releasing in cinemas nationwide on 17th October 2025, distributed by Cin√©polis India.
 
Produced by: Abhimanyu Singh and Roopali Singh (Contiloe Pictures)
Directed by: Raizada Rohit Jaising Vaid
 
Featuring a stellar voice cast:
 
Kunal Kapoor as Rama
Jimmy Shergill as Lakshman
Mouni Roy as Sita
Gulshan Grover as Raavan
 
This teaser offers a glimpse into grand battles, divine destiny, and the eternal fight between dharma and adharma, brought to life with state-of-the-art animation and spectacular visuals.
 
From the makers of State of Siege ‚Äì 26/11, State of Siege ‚Äì Temple Attack, Taj ‚Äì Divided by Blood, and Taj ‚Äì Reign of Revenge, Contiloe Pictures embarks on a new journey to redefine Indian mythological cinema.
 
Releasing in 3D this Diwali ‚Äì 17th October 2025.

Movie:  Khal Nayak (1993)
Singer: Alka Yagnik & Ila Arun
Composer: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi

Movie Credits:

Producer : Subhash Ghai

Lyrics:

Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶
Choli Ke Peechhe Kya Hai,
Choli Ke Peechhe
Choli Ke Peechhe Kya Hai,
Choli Ke Peechhe

Chunari Ke Niche

Yeh Dil Mein Dungi Mere Yar Ko, Pyar Ko
Aah Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶

Aashiq Purane Tere, Aashiq Purane
Ho Aashiq Mila Naa Aisa Hmmm,

Kya Karu Kya Karu
Hay Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶

Koyi Udhar Ko Khinche Kya Karu Kya Karu

Ku Ku Ku Ku Ku‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶
Ho‚Ä¶Jhumari Kaa Jumaru Ban Ja,

Payal Kaa, Ghungharu Ban Ja

Meri Salami Kar Le, Meri Ghulami Kar Le
Hoga Too Hoga Koyi

Soti Hoon Main

snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil unveils the full video "Vazhiyiraen", the latest single from the highly anticipated film Madharaasi, written and directed by A.R. Murugadoss. Featuring the charismatic Sivakarthikeyan and the graceful Rukmini Vasanth, Vazhiyiraen stands out as an emotionally rich and visually stunning track that beautifully captures themes of love, hope, and longing. With Anirudh Ravichander‚Äôs heartfelt composition and soul-touching vocals, the song resonates deeply, offering a cinematic musical experience that lingers long after it ends.

Set against picturesque visuals and brought to life by the tender chemistry between the lead pair, Vazhiyiraen is quickly becoming a fan favorite among Tamil romantic songs 2025. Perfect for those who enjoy melodious love songs, Anirudh hits, and lyrical storytelling, this track adds emotional depth to the Madharaasi soundtrack. Don't miss this musical gem that's already trending under #VazhiyiraenSong, a must-watch for fans of Sivakarthikeyan movies, AR Murugadoss direction, and Tamil film music at its finest.

‚ú®Kalaratri Mantra | Navratri Day 7 | Navdurga Mantra ‚ú®

Maa Kalaratri, the seventh form of Navdurga, is known as the fiercest and most powerful manifestation of Goddess Durga. She destroys negative energies, removes fear, and grants immense courage, strength, and protection to her devotees.

Chanting or listening to the Kalaratri Mantra during Navratri or daily sadhana is believed to bring fearlessness, spiritual upliftment, and divine blessings. Surrender to Maa Kalaratri and invite positivity, strength, and inner peace.

üôè Experience the divine energy of Maa Kalaratri with this sacred mantra.

snippet.title: I Went to FFMIC and Total Gaming Became CS Champion üèÜüî• Live Reaction üò≥
snippet.description:
Today, I witnessed one of the best comebacks in Free Fire history! After four years, the Free Fire India Max Cup returned, and Total Gaming pulled off an epic BOOYAH! In the finals against GodL, GodL had a 2-point lead in the best-of-five series. But Total Gaming made an incredible comeback, leveling the score 2-2. In the final match, with the score tied 5-5, Total Gaming clinched the victory in the last round. It was truly an epic comeback and one of the greatest moments in Free Fire‚Äôs history!

A big shoutout and congratulations to Ajju Bhai, Total Gaming, Fauji ajay mafia and Delete & all for their outstanding performance! Also, kudos to Jonty Gaming and NG Pros for their amazing gameplay. And let‚Äôs not forget Marco from the GodL team, whose sniping was absolutely top notch!

All the best to everyone in the battle royale matches today
